{"word":"H6567 - פָּרָשׁ - pârâsh - paw-rash' - Scatter","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פָּרָשׁ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pârâsh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>paw-rash'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Scatter"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிதறு, கடி, தீர்க்கம், தெளிவாக்கு, கொடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to make distinct, to declare, to distinguish, to separate"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to declare, to clarify"},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual) to be distinctly declared"},{"paragraph":"2) (Hiphil) to pierce, to sting"},{"paragraph":"3) (Niphal) to scatter"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>separate</i>, literally (to <i>disperse</i>) or figuratively (to <i>specify</i>); also (by implication) to <i>wound: - </i>scatter, declare, distinctly, shew, sting."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6567 - פָּרָשׁ - pârâsh - paw-rash'/6567\">H6567</a>, <a href=\"#/H6575 - פָּרָשָׁה - pârâshâh - paw-raw-shaw'/6575\">H6575</a>"}]}